title: Ep 29 - 10 Keys to a Successful Day
itunes:title: Ep 29 - 10 Keys to a Successful Day
description:
In this episode we cover and excerpt Dale Carnegie's book "How to Stop Worrying and Start Living" called "Just For Today." We cover the 10 steps for a successful day and make it a challenge to follow these steps, not just for today, but every day.
